  "template": "{SUBJ} ____ {OBJ} since {SINCE_CLAUSE}.",
  "example": "The fund manager has optimized the portfolio since the market correction occurred.",
  "explanation": "Use 'has' + past participle with 'he/she/it' and professional titles to describe actions from a past point to now. 'Since' indicates when the action started.",
